Edit platform/browser-extension/src/side-panel/components/FailedPluginCard.tsx (15 lines currently).

1. Change error text from 11px to `text-xs` (12px) for readability
2. Add `select-text` class to the error paragraph for copy support
3. Add a truncation pattern: show first 2 lines by default, with a 'Show more' / 'Show less' toggle. Use React state for expanded/collapsed. Truncate with `line-clamp-2` when collapsed.

Example:
```tsx
const [expanded, setExpanded] = useState(false);
// ...
<p className={`text-xs text-destructive/70 select-text ${expanded ? '' : 'line-clamp-2'}`}>{error}</p>
{error.length > 100 && (
  <button onClick={() => setExpanded(!expanded)} className="text-xs text-muted-foreground underline">
    {expanded ? 'Show less' : 'Show more'}
  </button>
)}
```
